In reality, in the eyes of informed individuals, you wouldn't even be considered a person; it's as simple as a piece of cake. You appear to be just one close-minded, uneducated person with zero education level

HistoryofIran, Pashtun history or tribes are not a fake story which made by iran like the Achaemenid Empire, fake Zabol in Iran, fake Naqsh-e Rostam in Iran, fake Khorasan provinces in Iran, and the transition from 'Aryan' to 'Iran,' among many other topics. If you lack knowledge about Pashtun tribes and persist in making unfounded accusations, it may be best to refrain from such baseless claims

Dear daal khor It's both perplexing and troubling when someone from outside our culture and heritage attempts to alter our tribal narratives without credible evidence or understanding. daal khor I urge you to refrain from disseminating inaccurate information. This isn't your community; please respect our history and traditions.
